verbose_text: Some of them like [18 F] Galacto-RGD, [18 F] Fluciclatide, [18 F] RGD-K5, [68 Ga] NOTA-RGD, [68 Ga] NOTA-PRGD2, [18 F] FPPRGD2, and [18 F] Alfatide II are currently under clinical investigations for the identification of malignant lesions and quantitative assessment of integrin alpha v beta 3 expression.
